<英文法規名稱>Regulations Governing Profit-seeking Enterprise Income Tax Exemption for Foreign Profit-seeking Enterprises Conducting Goods Storage and/or Simple Processing Operations in the Free Trade Zone of International Airport Park</英文法規名稱>
